<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Covid Cameroon</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/css/app.css") %>"/>
    <%= csrf_meta_tag() %>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/js/app.js") %>"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <section class="container-fluid">
        <nav role="phx-hero">
            <p>Bienvenue, petite application ou vous aurez les chiffres sur les donnations et sur les cas detectes. L'actualisation se fait en temps reel!
            <strong>Les donnations sont mises a jour automatiquement chaque 60 sec, </strong>
            <strong>Les statistiques d'infections toutes les 1H </strong>
            </p>
        </nav>
      </section>
    </header>
    <main role="main" class="container-fluid">
      <p class="text-center links">
        <%= link "Acceuil/Home", to: Routes.page_path(@conn, :index) %>
        <%= link "Stats", to: Routes.page_path(@conn, :stats) %>
        <%= link "Projections", to: Routes.page_path(@conn, :projections) %>
        <%= link "Se Consulter/Consult", to: Routes.page_path(@conn, :consult) %>
      </p>
      <p class="alert alert-info" role="alert"><%= get_flash(@conn, :info) %></p>
      <p class="alert alert-danger" role="alert"><%= get_flash(@conn, :error) %></p>
      <%= render @view_module, @view_template, assigns %>
      <small>Des questions ou suggestions, laissez moi un mail <a href="mailto:francktchowa@gmail.com">Franck Tchowa</a>  </small>
    </main>
    <!-- Global site tag (gtag.js) - Google Analytics -->
  <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=UA-82708913-4"></script>
  <script>
    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
    function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
    gtag('js', new Date());

    gtag('config', 'UA-82708913-4');
  </script>
  </body>
</html>
